25. Reddita, a vagne address to the powers, whoever they are, who control the fate of Paetus’ body. Possibly Aquilo and Neptune (ll. 13, 15) are included. Reddo (see note on 2. 1. 71) implies not restoration, but a giving of what is due, natural, or expected. All · kinds of duty therefore are appropriate to the word: here the notion is that a body is due to the earth, as much as that it is the duty of friends to bury it.
